<template>
    search{{ shopInfo }}
</template>

<script>
import { useRoute } from 'vue-router'
export default {
    name: 'Search',
    setup() {
        const route = useRoute()
        let shopInfo = route.params.shopInfo
        return {
            shopInfo
        }
    }
}
</script>

</style>
